mm_decref Point #1 rc=0 [stack-promotion.main]
  mm_free Point #1
    sl_free Point #1 size=48 class=4
mm_raw_alloc #R1 size=40
  sl_alloc size=40 class=4
mm_raw_free #R1
  sl_free size=48 class=4
```
